{
  "video_id": "OWYovDRt8tI",
  "title": "Jacque Fresco - Looking for Justice",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 400.0,
      "end_time": 3860.0,
      "text": "Which may or may not, but it depends on who I&#39;m talking to."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4000.0,
      "end_time": 6540.0,
      "text": "If I&#39;m talking to a bunch of firemen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6194.0,
      "end_time": 8860.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll say you guys sacrifice your life for the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9000.0,
      "end_time": 12419.0,
      "text": "but the real problem is: no fires."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12916.0,
      "end_time": 16995.0,
      "text": "\"If you did away with fires, I&#39;d lose my job.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17135.0,
      "end_time": 19262.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a threat there too."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19402.0,
      "end_time": 23531.0,
      "text": "I spoke to policemen years ago (I never told you this)."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 23885.0,
      "end_time": 26493.0,
      "text": "I spoke to about 50 policemen"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26633.0,
      "end_time": 30558.0,
      "text": "and I told them that they could be easily displaced."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30698.0,
      "end_time": 33599.0,
      "text": "They said \"Oh no, you&#39;ve got to have policemen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33739.0,
      "end_time": 36796.0,
      "text": "I began to proceed on how to displace them."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36936.0,
      "end_time": 39910.0,
      "text": "I put a kymograph in an automobile"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40500.0,
      "end_time": 44751.0,
      "text": "a rotary cylinder, electrically operated, with a needle on it"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44891.0,
      "end_time": 48619.0,
      "text": "so when you get to a zone of 60 mph, if you do 65"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48759.0,
      "end_time": 52503.0,
      "text": "the kymograph registers every violation you made."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52643.0,
      "end_time": 55880.0,
      "text": "You have to mail that in every month."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56200.0,
      "end_time": 59200.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t need traffic cops out there on motorcycles."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59142.0,
      "end_time": 61989.0,
      "text": "Every violation will be indicated by that."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62129.0,
      "end_time": 64860.0,
      "text": "They said to me \"That&#39;ll put us out of work.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65000.0,
      "end_time": 68644.0,
      "text": "I said \"Yes, you&#39;re easy to put out of work, easy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68784.0,
      "end_time": 71433.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no job that&#39;s secure. Nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71573.0,
      "end_time": 75478.0,
      "text": "Even surgery will be out 15 to 20 years from now."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75618.0,
      "end_time": 77812.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just a matter of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77952.0,
      "end_time": 82563.0,
      "text": "If we live that long, if we live to the next 20 or 30 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83280.0,
      "end_time": 87330.0,
      "text": "the system will be very bad, if we continue the way we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87173.0,
      "end_time": 91527.0,
      "text": "I see nothing to stop people from really stopping polluting."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92210.0,
      "end_time": 94464.0,
      "text": "The Peace Ship that goes out"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94604.0,
      "end_time": 97277.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t want the Japanese killing whales"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97417.0,
      "end_time": 100209.0,
      "text": "and we kill chickens and cows"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100349.0,
      "end_time": 104860.0,
      "text": "because we eat them and the Japanese eat fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105000.0,
      "end_time": 108540.0,
      "text": "They eat certain things we don&#39;t eat and there&#39;s money in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108680.0,
      "end_time": 110902.0,
      "text": "Why shouldn&#39;t they kill the whales?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111420.0,
      "end_time": 114751.0,
      "text": "Who are you to say \"Don&#39;t kill the whales? \" Don&#39;t kill anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114891.0,
      "end_time": 118689.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t kill a fly because they&#39;re here, made by God."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118829.0,
      "end_time": 121375.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re killing all God&#39;s creatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121516.0,
      "end_time": 124576.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no way to deal with that subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124716.0,
      "end_time": 127556.0,
      "text": "The Peace Corp wants peace"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127696.0,
      "end_time": 131749.0,
      "text": "but they don&#39;t know that peace is a product of culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132190.0,
      "end_time": 134745.0,
      "text": "Peace is the interval between wars."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134885.0,
      "end_time": 138960.0,
      "text": "There never has been peace as a system."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138236.0,
      "end_time": 141185.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s always been wars. That&#39;s a natural thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141325.0,
      "end_time": 144600.0,
      "text": "Natural for humans, the way they are today."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145510.0,
      "end_time": 148679.0,
      "text": "Where do they get it? From the Bible: \"Revenge is sweet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148820.0,
      "end_time": 152263.0,
      "text": "The Jews were permitted to kill people, have sex with people"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 152404.0,
      "end_time": 155271.0,
      "text": "that were non-Jews. Did you know that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155411.0,
      "end_time": 158469.0,
      "text": "I told you about Salem, Massachusetts, didn&#39;t I?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 159742.0,
      "end_time": 162164.0,
      "text": "Witch hunts? - Yeah, I know all about it..."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 162304.0,
      "end_time": 165547.0,
      "text": "- Did you know that if you found a witch you got their possessions"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165687.0,
      "end_time": 168210.0,
      "text": "their bank and land? - Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168161.0,
      "end_time": 171377.0,
      "text": "It was good to find as many witches as you can!"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 171517.0,
      "end_time": 175646.0,
      "text": "The system is so... Where the hell do you start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175786.0,
      "end_time": 178335.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s aberrated all the way through."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 178475.0,
      "end_time": 180984.0,
      "text": "If a guy says \"I believe in the free enterprise system\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 181125.0,
      "end_time": 183270.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t even want to take the time out."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183410.0,
      "end_time": 186446.0,
      "text": "If they say \"Do you feel the system can be improved"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186586.0,
      "end_time": 188414.0,
      "text": "and how can that be done?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188554.0,
      "end_time": 192860.0,
      "text": "How would you deal with corruption amongst the politicians?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 193000.0,
      "end_time": 196392.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d ask questions, millions of them, if they were sane."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 196532.0,
      "end_time": 198235.0,
      "text": "If people come from another world"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198375.0,
      "end_time": 201251.0,
      "text": "if they&#39;re that smart, to make that journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201391.0,
      "end_time": 205215.0,
      "text": "what you say to them is \"What do you think I ought to know?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 205355.0,
      "end_time": 208450.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t talk to them about \"You got a wife and two kids?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208185.0,
      "end_time": 211621.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not interested in that shit. What do you think I ought to know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 211761.0,
      "end_time": 213634.0,
      "text": "If they&#39;re more advanced"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 213774.0,
      "end_time": 217312.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ll tell you what you ought to know, if they can do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 217452.0,
      "end_time": 219198.0,
      "text": "You know what I mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 220312.0,
      "end_time": 222444.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got a tough job in front of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 222584.0,
      "end_time": 226705.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;d rather have a tough job than go along with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 227243.0,
      "end_time": 230488.0,
      "text": "- I agree - If I wind up in jail, all right"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 230628.0,
      "end_time": 234859.0,
      "text": "but if you&#39;re not attached to things, like the buildings we have here:"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 235000.0,
      "end_time": 238248.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not attached to them. I do all I can in them"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 238388.0,
      "end_time": 241721.0,
      "text": "but if the government takes them over because they don&#39;t like the direction"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 241861.0,
      "end_time": 243780.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s possible, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 243920.0,
      "end_time": 248483.0,
      "text": "You have to include the possible or the highly probable"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 248624.0,
      "end_time": 251366.0,
      "text": "and you might get arrested or beaten up"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 251506.0,
      "end_time": 254533.0,
      "text": "because they think you&#39;re a communist. Do you understand?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 254673.0,
      "end_time": 260720.0,
      "text": "People don&#39;t have enough of a value system to see where you differ from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 260716.0,
      "end_time": 264860.0,
      "text": "\"All Japanese look alike. All niggers look alike.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 265488.0,
      "end_time": 267883.0,
      "text": "When I was a kid, that was the thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 268230.0,
      "end_time": 269860.0,
      "text": "When a Jap appeared in town"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 270000.0,
      "end_time": 273121.0,
      "text": "we used to run down the street and look at him as kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 273261.0,
      "end_time": 275896.0,
      "text": "We used to do terrible things. We used to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 276360.0,
      "end_time": 279914.0,
      "text": "\"Jimmy&#39;s sister is a cripple. \" Did you know that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 280540.0,
      "end_time": 283787.0,
      "text": "Normal kids, how can they be conditioned to do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 283928.0,
      "end_time": 287104.0,
      "text": "Imagine kids that are insensitive"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 288362.0,
      "end_time": 290769.0,
      "text": "to a blind person. They trip them."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 292189.0,
      "end_time": 296629.0,
      "text": "Many cerebral insufficients were walking down the street when I was a kid"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 296769.0,
      "end_time": 298633.0,
      "text": "they were not hospitalized."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 298773.0,
      "end_time": 301289.0,
      "text": "Kids used to give them horse shit and say \"Eat it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 301429.0,
      "end_time": 303532.0,
      "text": "The guy would eat it."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 304158.0,
      "end_time": 306270.0,
      "text": "They thought \"Hey, this guy eats horse shit!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 306410.0,
      "end_time": 309284.0,
      "text": "The kids had no knowledge, no training."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 309424.0,
      "end_time": 311195.0,
      "text": "They were very cruel"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 311335.0,
      "end_time": 313789.0,
      "text": "but they were normal kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 313929.0,
      "end_time": 317188.0,
      "text": "\"Did you ever see that, the idiot in town?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 318000.0,
      "end_time": 319972.0,
      "text": "I encountered that."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 320112.0,
      "end_time": 323564.0,
      "text": "I built a model airplane and I put it on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 323704.0,
      "end_time": 326988.0,
      "text": "One of the town insufficients was coming by"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 327128.0,
      "end_time": 328705.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d wait"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 329350.0,
      "end_time": 331691.0,
      "text": "so I could see if he&#39;d be amused by that"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 331831.0,
      "end_time": 335191.0,
      "text": "and he came over and wrecked it completely."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 335810.0,
      "end_time": 337702.0,
      "text": "I learned a lot that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 337842.0,
      "end_time": 340539.0,
      "text": "I thought he might be interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 341178.0,
      "end_time": 343645.0,
      "text": "I was looking for justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 343785.0,
      "end_time": 346658.0,
      "text": "Looking for justice will kill you. There&#39;s no such thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 346798.0,
      "end_time": 348708.0,
      "text": "Whatever happens is real."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 348848.0,
      "end_time": 351503.0,
      "text": "What you think should have happened is not real."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 351643.0,
      "end_time": 356464.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re disappointed, not in the world, but in your value system."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 356604.0,
      "end_time": 359859.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s your value system that&#39;s screwed up, not the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 360000.0,
      "end_time": 363780.0,
      "text": "The world is normally screwed up by time."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 363920.0,
      "end_time": 367471.0,
      "text": "If you say \"That&#39;s terrible what people did Wednesday."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 367611.0,
      "end_time": 370618.0,
      "text": "They killed a black guy and he was the wrong guy!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 371419.0,
      "end_time": 373806.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s within probability."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 373947.0,
      "end_time": 376246.0,
      "text": "Whatever happens is real. Can you remember that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 376386.0,
      "end_time": 379550.0,
      "text": "What you think should have happened is not."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 379894.0,
      "end_time": 382760.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;ve been fair to my wife, decent."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 382216.0,
      "end_time": 386485.0,
      "text": "I bought her everything she ever asked for, she ran away with the milkman.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 386625.0,
      "end_time": 389682.0,
      "text": "So what are you looking for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 389822.0,
      "end_time": 394185.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t know your wife&#39;s value systems that well, is what it means"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394325.0,
      "end_time": 396860.0,
      "text": "or you don&#39;t know enough about people."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 398823.0,
      "end_time": 402270.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s very hard to accept, \"Whatever happens is real.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 402411.0,
      "end_time": 404833.0,
      "text": "You go in for an examination one day and the doctor says"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 404973.0,
      "end_time": 409131.0,
      "text": "\"You&#39;ve got the last stages of cancer. You should have come much earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 409271.0,
      "end_time": 413616.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got about 4 months to live. Wrap up your problems.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 413756.0,
      "end_time": 416909.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very hard for people to say \"I see.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 419305.0,
      "end_time": 421499.0,
      "text": "\"But I&#39;m only 40 years old!"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 421639.0,
      "end_time": 425635.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m only a kid and I&#39;m bald. I&#39;ve lost my hair from radiation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 426937.0,
      "end_time": 430669.0,
      "text": "Kids say \"That&#39;s not fair. I haven&#39;t even begun to live yet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 430809.0,
      "end_time": 433763.0,
      "text": "The mother says \"That&#39;s not fair\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 433903.0,
